    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's good to hear, but we've had issues with other brands claiming the same thing and then seeing the charge drop significantly after about 14-16 hours of continuous work. Do you have any specific data or test reports showing they actually hit that 24-hour mark under a heavy load, or is that just the standard rating?",
